rooms.roomDescription: Two additional bedrooms on main level

data.description: Feel like you are in the country at the edge of town. Beautiful Maple Burlap hardwood floors through out the first floor except the two bathrooms that are tile. Nice granite countertops.  Wood burning fireplace in the great room. Wooden deck with great views of the 1.92 acres. Several trees on this lot with a lot of possibilities for outdoor activities (firepits, motorized vehicles, gardening, etc.). In the basement is a family room with a fireplace utilizing a buck wood burning stove, a toy room, garage and plenty of storage room.
